Format:  @{b}TAPDELAY@{ub}=@{i}<boolean>@{ui}


Sets the state of the @{"Settings->Misc->Delay during TAP load" LINK Misc_FlashDelay}
 preference.






@{"Tooltypes index" LINK ToolTypes}

@ENDNODE
@NODE Arg_UseFKeys "USEFKEYS Argument"


Format:  @{b}USEFKEYS@{ub}=@{i}<boolean>@{ui}


Sets the state of the @{"Settings->Misc->Use F-Keys" LINK Misc_UseFKeys} preference.







