ASp has been written from scratch in 680x0 asm using HiSoft's Devpac 3.18.


Current development machine spec: A1200, 64MHz 68060, 128MB, 1GB HDD.


Some of the data structures have been created in TurboCalc2 and processed
using programs compiled with VBCC.


Total size of all source and data files used to create ASp: 1.5MB.

Size of asm source files for final assembly: 978KB.

Approximate assembly time in Devpac: 8 sec.



@ENDNODE
